data.description: Don't miss this opportunity! Welcome home to this 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath house in the desirable community of Country Lakes.  The home was fully renovated in 2019 paying attention to detail with chair rail, a textured wall, and custom tile work. Installed in 2019 a new roof, new kitchen, new master bath, new floors and carpets, and a new A/C.   The Beautiful open kitchen has stainless steel appliances. As a Bonus there is a sunroom in back of house. Make an offer and you could be living here making memories.  Pictures are taken prior to tenant moving in property.
